---
// Benefits.astro - Sección de beneficios del seguro de salud
---

<section id="beneficios" class="py-16 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Icono y título central -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 bg-pacifico-blue rounded-full mb-6">
        <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M12 2C13.1 2 14 2.9 14 4C14 5.1 13.1 6 12 6C10.9 6 10 5.1 10 4C10 2.9 10.9 2 12 2ZM21 9V7L15 7V9C15 11.8 12.8 14 10 14S5 11.8 5 14V16C5 18.2 6.8 20 9 20H15C17.2 20 19 18.2 19 16V15C21.2 15 22 12.2 22 10C22 10 21 9 21 9Z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">
        Con un <span class="text-pacifico-blue">Seguro<br>de Salud</span>, podrás tener:
      </h2>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Grid de beneficios -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Beneficio 1: Consultas médicas -->
      <div class="text-center group">
        <div class="bg-pacifico-gray rounded-2xl p-8 h-64 flex flex-col items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-pacifico-blue to-pacifico-light-blue rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M14.8 12L16 10.8L14.8 9.6L13.6 10.8L14.8 12ZM9.6 17.2L10.8 16L9.6 14.8L8.4 16L9.6 17.2ZM15.2 17.2L16.4 16L15.2 14.8L14 16L15.2 17.2ZM10.4 12L11.6 10.8L10.4 9.6L9.2 10.8L10.4 12ZM12 22C17.52 22 22 17.52 22 12S17.52 2 12 2 2 6.48 2 12 6.48 22 12 22ZM12 20C7.59 20 4 16.41 4 12S7.59 4 12 4 20 7.59 20 12 16.41 20 12 20Z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Consultas médicas</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Acceso a médicos especialistas y consultas preventivas</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Beneficio 2: Emergencias -->
      <div class="text-center group">
        <div class="bg-pacifico-gray rounded-2xl p-8 h-64 flex flex-col items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-pacifico-pink to-red-400 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 2L13.09 8.26L22 9L13.09 9.74L12 16L10.91 9.74L2 9L10.91 8.26L12 2ZM4 14L6 20L8 14H4ZM16 14L18 20L20 14H16Z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Atención de emergencias</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Cobertura 24/7 para situaciones de emergencia</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Beneficio 3: Hospitalización -->
      <div class="text-center group">
        <div class="bg-pacifico-gray rounded-2xl p-8 h-64 flex flex-col items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-pacifico-blue to-pacifico-dark-blue rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M19 3H5C3.9 3 3 3.9 3 5V19C3 20.1 3.9 21 5 21H19C20.1 21 21 20.1 21 19V5C21 3.9 20.1 3 19 3ZM18 18H6V6H18V18ZM14 10H16V14H14V16H10V14H8V10H10V8H14V10Z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Hospitalización</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Cobertura completa para internamiento y cirugías</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Texto adicional -->
    <div class="text-center mt-12">
      <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Y muchos beneficios más que te ayudarán a mantener tu tranquilidad y la de tu familia ante cualquier eventualidad de salud.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
